title: Public Schools Are GARBAGE, and We Have PROOF!!
description:
Ding dong, Liz Cheney's political career is dead. One of the last of Donald Trump's foes has been vanquished, and we're here to revel in her misery — and the media's. Also, with kids going back to school, we give you all the reasons why public schools suck. And in Minneapolis, you can get fired for being white. #Backtoschool #Publicschools #LizCheney
